Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:30.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:37.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:39.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:42.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:47.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这份心情无法释怀  无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:52.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}越是想着不可以  就陷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:57.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}变得连自己都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:01.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不如相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:05.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:08.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都决定要伴随在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:09.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:14.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:17.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}命运要我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:25.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要我止步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:27.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:29.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这理由却还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:34.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可为你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂
