Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要妨碍我着地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是想接住你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是来参加「Society」的舞会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐  你露得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来参加舞会  露这点算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼服怎么样  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可爱哦  很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这舞会也算是遗物使的表现舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以代替自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是LV10却没登录在协会里  你在这可算是一个谜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我不太想招人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到以后的事  你也得见见这种世面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  先来给我做伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有萝丝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是蓝胡子男爵  A级以上遗物的收藏家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个爱用强硬手段和钱的讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样为收藏家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位牧原先生是在十多年前被人偷了收藏品的可怜人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说连孩子也一起被掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他因为太过伤心所以离开了协会才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是石津先生  专门收藏关于占卜的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的人都来参加了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是七尾英理子小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫斋木  是个新人收藏家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的机构让我感受很深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机构？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始寻找遗物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经夺回了一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这是A级的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是「True Love」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须集齐2个才能发挥效力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我还没找到呢  您有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我这新人还帮不上忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这会场里竟然会出现3个A级的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为只有男爵的油灯和女士的戒指而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝了会报的采访
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不像保住先生那样总有保镖在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥德爱啊  专门偷A级遗物的通缉犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有狼耳和尾巴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是为了掩饰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使人把印象集中在这些东西上而把相貌忽视了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:06:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  所以目击情报才会那么少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  能请您把联系方式给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有另一半耳环的情报我会向您报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么告辞了  能跟您交谈真是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚才见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是来参加舞会的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收藏家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也是遗物使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也？那你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保住先生  这会让我们为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会赔你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天你们来找我要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  刚才那女孩子是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  你冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上快上快上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  站…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…奥德爱？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇定下来  把灯开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  为什么你要救奥德爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是她的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是用警棒打女孩子有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一会再解释  不要离开这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系前台  封锁宾馆周边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了  竟然录口供录了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我救了她这也是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然发生了很多事  不过舞会本身还是挺有趣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我保护这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这耳环有什么能力啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有能听取「真实」的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把两个都戴上后交谈  就能读心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光一个的话就只是个普通的耳环而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有女性遗物使才能用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性才能用？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且听说还必须是希望了解所爱之人的心的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有原本持有它的女性被男人深深伤害了的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些情报都不怎么靠谱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来还是要集齐才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准花心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  让开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户仓先生给我的束缚用的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说原材料是遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪龙司粘在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英理子姐的瞄准能力太次了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  花心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来足够强韧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把这家伙的颈动脉咬破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐  阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就把龙司放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静点  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我念了咒文也解不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？就算是实验品这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  户仓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…他说等一天或许就能解下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  这也就是说我们有一天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不少东西要问你呢  奥德爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要招了  不管什么刑罚我都会忍下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这耳朵是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想招了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告诉我年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这年纪就到处去偷遗物  是受人指使的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说被人威胁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我自己干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么可能理解  「Society」的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个混蛋唆使你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁  竟然让这样的孩子去偷东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙肯定是个垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说主人的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那家伙让你犯罪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连学校都不让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？看看这野兽的身体  看看这纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他养大了连双亲都抛弃了的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上流着被诅咒的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情高亢时就会变成这半人半兽的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她全招了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你主人为什么要偷我的耳环
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  英理子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么搞成这种状况？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们连在一起  还能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不碰怎么洗啊  乖乖就范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少快点洗完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司就让萝丝来帮你洗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为得死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要死了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你那么有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛茸茸  毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛茸茸的到处摆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  别做人家讨厌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你的名字呢？奥德爱不是真名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人叫我爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么毫不在意地摸我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得恶心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服哦  毛茸茸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这令人忌讳的野兽之力  这恶心的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要说这个的话  萝丝她就…看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝是红龙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  看  看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  你什么时候能飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想给龙司惊喜所以就努力练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的手上有龙纹  很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你的纹章一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们讨好我也没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能相信的只有主人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是受那人指使去偷东西的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被利用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是赞同了主人的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  你不能呆在那种环境里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开你的主人比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  不闭上你的嘴我就咬断你脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不出这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候你不是救了小猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止这个  在会场的时候你也护住了老奶奶是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是个坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你们说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  看  看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝  够了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你到底藏了多少酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下毒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是龙司做的  我只是热一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会干那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说不定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不饿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不饿！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过都做好了就喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  这奇怪的声音  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吓到萝丝的  还是喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  这次就当特例
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫古森  当时55岁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LV9的遗物使  遗物研究的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这家伙就是黑幕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是非常优秀的研究者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在研究的过程中接触了禁忌领域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让超过二十人无法醒来之后带着大量的遗物消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设这家伙就是那女孩的主人  那他目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  关于他的资料和数据在「Society」里也是超级机密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕和那女孩的…跟15年前的上级机关有什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫古森的家伙已经70岁左右了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人还很年轻  而且不是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他让你去偷东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗物不应该被一部分人独占
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让全世界的人都受惠才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过主人因私利私欲而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧拜访你们很抱歉  因为我想尽快把它送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  本该由我来拜访你才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  这真的是「True Love」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我调查了一下发现朋友收藏着它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快请过目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  好东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱  你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是龙司君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  这东西解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…古森？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字我早就抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上他一起吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:40.12,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回「狼群的真相」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫爱  和主人两人一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的时候就自己玩词语接龙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱  墨水  蜡笔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接不下去了  我输了


